To whom it may deeply concern,

I am guessing that you meant to come here, rather than it being a massive coincidence that you typed in a random URL and landed on this page, in which case, what are the chances of that?

Disclaimer: that was a retorical question, although if you are so inclined to work it out, be my guest.

Welcome to the sometimes interesting, otherwise nonsensical rantings of a software developer.

I hope you enjoy your satay, if you're having a Chinese meal, otherwise I hope you enjoy your stay.

Disclaimer: Yes, I wrote stay wrong initially, but decided to keep it and incorporate it.

Kindest of regards,

Gareth.
